comment:
* Information about how the user has interacted with a given notification.
 * @hide

variables.name: DISMISSAL_NOT_DISMISSED
variables.comment: * Notification has not been dismissed yet.

variables.name: DISMISSAL_OTHER
variables.comment:
* Notification has been dismissed from a {@link NotificationListenerService} or the app
     * itself.

variables.name: DISMISSAL_PEEK
variables.comment: * Notification has been dismissed while peeking.

variables.name: DISMISSAL_AOD
variables.comment: * Notification has been dismissed from always on display.

variables.name: DISMISSAL_SHADE
variables.comment: * Notification has been dismissed from the notification shade.

variables.name: DISMISSAL_BUBBLE
variables.comment:
* Notification has been dismissed as a bubble.
     * @hide

variables.name: DISMISSAL_LOCKSCREEN
variables.comment:
* Notification has been dismissed from the lock screen.
     * @hide

variables.name: DISMISS_SENTIMENT_UNKNOWN
variables.comment:
* No information is available about why this notification was dismissed, or the notification
     * isn't dismissed yet.

variables.name: DISMISS_SENTIMENT_NEGATIVE
variables.comment: * The user indicated while dismissing that they did not like the notification.

variables.name: DISMISS_SENTIMENT_NEUTRAL
variables.comment:
* The user didn't indicate one way or another how they felt about the notification while
     * dismissing it.

variables.name: DISMISS_SENTIMENT_POSITIVE
variables.comment: * The user indicated while dismissing that they did like the notification.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
public boolean hasSeen()
methods.comment: * Returns whether the user has seen this notification at least once.

methods.name: public void setSeen()
methods.comment: * Records that the user as seen this notification at least once.

methods.name: public boolean hasExpanded()
methods.comment: * Returns whether the user has expanded this notification at least once.

methods.name: public void setExpanded()
methods.comment: * Records that the user has expanded this notification at least once.

methods.name: public boolean hasDirectReplied()
methods.comment:
* Returns whether the user has replied to a notification that has a
     * {@link android.app.Notification.Action.Builder#addRemoteInput(RemoteInput) direct reply} at
     * least once.

methods.name: public void setDirectReplied()
public boolean hasSmartReplied()
methods.comment: * Returns whether the user has replied to a notification that has a smart reply at least once.

methods.name: public void setSmartReplied()
methods.comment: * Records that the user has replied to a notification that has a smart reply at least once.

methods.name: public boolean hasSnoozed()
methods.comment: * Returns whether the user has snoozed this notification at least once.

methods.name: public void setSnoozed()
methods.comment: * Records that the user has snoozed this notification at least once.

methods.name: public boolean hasViewedSettings()
methods.comment:
* Returns whether the user has viewed the in-shade settings for this notification at least
     * once.

methods.name: public void setViewedSettings()
methods.comment: * Records that the user has viewed the in-shade settings for this notification at least once.

methods.name: public boolean hasInteracted()
methods.comment: * Returns whether the user has interacted with this notification beyond having viewed it.

methods.name: public int getDismissalSurface()
methods.comment: * Returns from which surface the notification was dismissed.

methods.name: public void setDismissalSurface(@DismissalSurface int dismissalSurface)
methods.comment: * Returns from which surface the notification was dismissed.

methods.name: public void setDismissalSentiment(@DismissalSentiment int dismissalSentiment)
methods.comment:
* Records whether the user indicated how they felt about a notification before or
     * during dismissal.

methods.name: public int getDismissalSentiment()
methods.comment: * Returns how the user indicated they felt about a notification before or during dismissal.

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
